TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclN1YldlYXBv.name: Work the Angles
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclN1YldlYXBv.desc:
Who's the best shot with an Angle Shooter?
Let's find out.
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclN1YldlYXBv.regulation:
Aim is the name of the game! Bring your Angle Shooters for this battle of the best bounces.

・ You can only use weapons that come with the Angle Shooter sub weapon.
・ Angle Shooter damage will be greatly increased for all players.
・ Angle Shooter ink consumption will also be greatly increased for all players.
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Nb250aGx5TGVhZ3Vl.name: Monthly Challenge
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Nb250aGx5TGVhZ3Vl.desc: Aim for the highest Challenge Power!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Nb250aGx5TGVhZ3Vl.regulation:
How high can you get your Challenge Power this month?

・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled in Turf War battles. Secondary gear abilities will have no effect!
・ There will be no limits on gear abilities in Anarchy Battle modes!

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.name: Barrel of Splats
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.desc:
Muster as much firepower as you can
in this battle of the splatlings!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.regulation:
Bring the heat with your best splatling loadout, and see who's left standing.

・ Players can only choose different varieties of splatlings!
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Nb2RpZmllZF9SYWlu.name: Modded Rainmaker Test-Fire
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Nb2RpZmllZF9SYWlu.desc:
Sheldon has been tinkering with the
Rainmaker, and he wants you to test it!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Nb2RpZmllZF9SYWlu.regulation:
Help test Sheldon's latest modifications to the Rainmaker weapon, and get some good battling in while you're at it!

・ All battles will be in Rainmaker mode.
・ Fully charged Rainmaker shots will now fire in three directions!
・ The abilities of the player holding the Rainmaker will be boosted!
・ The Rainmaker will explode 30 seconds after being picked up. Watch out!
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9T.name: Reefslider Rally
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9T.desc:
Rev up your Reefsliders, and ride
into battle!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9T.regulation:
Who's got two pectoral fins and is ready to ride? Literally every player in this Challenge!

・ You can only use weapons that come with the Reefslider special.
・ The special gauge will fill quickly all by itself!
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Db3N0dW1lUGFydHk=.name: Sheldon's Dress-Up Showdown
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Db3N0dW1lUGFydHk=.desc:
Raid Sheldon's arsenal and closet for
random weapons and outfits!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Db3N0dW1lUGFydHk=.regulation:
Make the most of a random assortment of Sheldon's weapons and outfits in this come-as-you-are Challenge!

・ You'll be assigned an outfit and weapon at the start of battle.
・ Your loadout will completely change with each subsequent battle!
・ Sheldon is graciously loaning all of the equipment, so you don't need to own the items you're using. You also don't get to keep them.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1HZXlzZXI=.name: Oh My Gush
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1HZXlzZXI=.desc:
The stages you know and love are now
filled with gushers. How will you use them?
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1HZXlzZXI=.regulation:
Where did all those gushers come from? Might as well make the most of them!

・ Gushers have appeared in the stage!
・ Attack a gusher to make it erupt with your color of ink.
・ You can use them to hide or climb.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.name: Fastest Blasters
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.desc:
Bring your blasters and get ready
for blastoff!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.regulation:
Have you mastered blasters? Let's see what you can do!

・ Players can only choose different varieties of blasters!
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Nb2RpZmllZF9Ub3dl.name: Towering Tower Control
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Nb2RpZmllZF9Ub3dl.desc:
The tower is way bigger than before!
All aboard!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Nb2RpZmllZF9Ub3dl.regulation:
Can you control the biggest tower ever?

・ All battles will be in Tower Control mode.
・ The tower is now enormous—your whole team can fit!
・ Coordinate with teammates to attack the enemy base.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9V.name: Too Many Trizookas!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9V.regulation:
Can you defeat a Trizooka user with a Trizooka of your own?! Now's the time to find out!

・ You can only use weapons that come with the Trizooka special.
・ The special gauge will fill quickly all by itself!
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1SYWlubWFrZXJEcm9w.name: Making It Rain...Here?
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1SYWlubWFrZXJEcm9w.desc:
Try out the Rainmaker in places it was never
meant to be used!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1SYWlubWFrZXJEcm9w.regulation:
See what you can do with the Rainmaker in a regular battle!

・ The mode will not be Rainmaker.
・ The Rainmaker will appear in the center of the stage.
・ Any player who obtains the Rainmaker can use it to their advantage!
・ If the player holding the Rainmaker is defeated, the Rainmaker will return to the center of the stage.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.name: Fully Charged
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.desc:
Time to see if you're a hotshot
with your favorite charger!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.regulation:
Bring your favorite charger and take your shot!

・ Players can only choose different varieties of chargers!
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclN1YldlYXBv.name: Curling Hurl
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclN1YldlYXBv.desc:
Toss out jumbo-sized Curling Bombs in
this frenetic Challenge!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclN1YldlYXBv.regulation:
Make way for the giant Curling Bombs as they glide across the battlefield.

・ You can only use weapons that come with the Curling Bomb sub weapon.
・ Curling Bombs will be enlarged!
・ Curling Bomb contact damage will be greatly increased for all players.
・ Their explosion size will be greatly increased too!
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1QYWlyQ3Vw.name: Duel of Dynamic Duos
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1QYWlyQ3Vw.desc: See what you can do as a duo!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1QYWlyQ3Vw.regulation:
Team chemistry is the name of the game in fast-paced two vs. two battles!

・ Explore new strategies as you try to become the top team on the map!
・ Respawn time will be shortened!
・ You can participate as a team of 2 or solo.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled!

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.name: Dualies at Ten Paces
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.desc:
Enter a battlefield filled with slippery
customers in this all-dualies war!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.regulation:
Stick and move with the best of 'em in this dualies dustup!

・ Players can only choose different varieties of dualies.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Sb2xsZXJCcnVzaFNw.name: Full Stream Ahead
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Sb2xsZXJCcnVzaFNw.desc:
Stampede over your opponents with even
faster rollers and brushes!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1Sb2xsZXJCcnVzaFNw.regulation:
Rollers and brushes move faster than ever. The ink race is on!

・ Players can only choose different varieties of rollers or brushes.
・ All players have greatly increased ink speed.
・ Ink consumption while inking will also be greatly increased for all players.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.name: Brella Good
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.desc: Come back with your brella or on it!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.regulation:
It's time for a brellabration! Are you a canopy or a can't-opy?

・ Players can only choose different varieties of brellas.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9V.name: Ultra Stamp Rally
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9V.desc: Go on a stampage with your Ultra Stamp!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9V.regulation:
Deliver beatdowns left and right in this Ultra Stamp Challenge!

・ You can only use weapons with the Ultra Stamp special.
・ The special gauge will fill quickly all by itself!
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary gear abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclN1YldlYXBv.name: Splat Bomb Rush
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclN1YldlYXBv.desc: Let the Splat Bombs fly in this free-for-all!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclN1YldlYXBv.regulation:
It's Splat Bombs away in this explosive Challenge!

・ You can only use weapons with the Splat Bomb sub weapon.
・ Splat Bomb ink consumption will be cut in half!
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1SYW5kb21XZWFwb25B.name: Sheldon's Gear-Ability Shuffle
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1SYW5kb21XZWFwb25B.desc:
Let Sheldon pick your loadout for a battle
of random weapons and gear abilities!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1SYW5kb21XZWFwb25B.regulation:
Make the most of a random assortment of Sheldon's weapons and gear abilities in this test of adaptability!

・ You'll be assigned gear abilities and a weapon at the start of battle.
・ One gear ability you receive will be set to maximum power!
・ Three secondary gear abilities will also be assigned, regardless of the available slots on your gear.
・ Once the battle ends, your gear's previous abilities will be restored.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclNwZWNpYWxX.name: Bucket of Crab Tanks
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclNwZWNpYWxX.desc: Crab Tanks on the loose! Strafe to safety!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlclNwZWNpYWxX.regulation:
Whether faster Crab Tanks are your dream or nightmare, now they're real!

・ You can only use weapons with the Crab Tank special.
・ The sideways walking speed of the Crab Tank will be greatly increased!
・ Your speed when rolling with the ZL Button will not change.
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary gear abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlckJlYWNvbg==.name: Super Jump-a-thon
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlckJlYWNvbg==.desc:
Super Jump up and away! Stand by your
teammates with their Squid Beakons!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TdXBlckJlYWNvbg==.regulation:
Never fight alone with these high-speed Super Jumps to your allies' Squid Beakons!

・ You can only use weapons with the Squid Beakon sub weapon.
・ Super Jumps are much faster!
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled, except for Quick Super Jump and Sub Power Up. Secondary gear abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.name: Supreme Sloshers
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.desc: Go forth and slosher the opposition!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.regulation:
Do your slosher strats have what it takes? Let's find out!

・ Players can only choose different varieties of sloshers.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1IaWdoSnVtcA==.name: Extreme Jump Battle
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1IaWdoSnVtcA==.desc: Jump power UP! See where it takes you!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1IaWdoSnVtcA==.regulation:
With the ability to jump higher than ever, you can explore new attack routes and strategies on the map!

・ Jump power will be greatly increased for all players.
・ Armor durability will be increased after doing a Squid Spawn.
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1SYW5kb21XZWFwb24=.name: The Sheldon Sampler Challenge
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1SYW5kb21XZWFwb24=.desc: Make the most of random weapons!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1SYW5kb21XZWFwb24=.regulation:
"I'm happy to loan out my entire inventory for this Challenge. Try something different, and see if you find a new favorite!"
-Sheldon

・ Weapons will be randomly assigned before each battle.
・ Sheldon will be graciously loaning these weapons out, so don't worry if you don't own every possible weapon.
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled!

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.name: Art Battle for the Ages
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.desc: It's rollers vs. brushes for bragging rights!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1XZWFwb25MaW1pdGVk.regulation:
This Challenge only allows rollers and brushes—it's not for the faint of art!

・ The only weapons you can use are rollers or brushes!
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled!

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1EZWVwRm9n.name: Foggy Notion
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1EZWVwRm9n.desc: The stakes are high in low-vis battles!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1EZWVwRm9n.regulation:
Can you use the fog cover to your advantage?

・ The stage will be shrouded in fog through the battle.
・ However, the density of the fog will change as the battle goes on!
・ Both primary and secondary abilities will be enabled!

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9a.name: Zip-to-It Zipcaster Challenge
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9a.desc: Fly free with unlimited Zipcaster use!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9a.regulation:
This Challenge asks: Where would you go and how would you battle if you could use the Zipcaster to your heart's content?

・ You can only use weapons that come with the Zipcaster special.
・ The special gauge will fill quickly all by itself!
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9K.name: Inkjets for Everyone!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1TcGVjaWFsUnVzaF9K.regulation:
Take to the air with your Inkjet special, and splat it out in the sky!

・ You can only use weapons that come with the Inkjet special.
・ The special gauge will fill quickly all by itself!
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary abilities will have no effect.

TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1GYXN0TW92ZQ==.name: Swim It to Win It
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1GYXN0TW92ZQ==.desc: Swim speed up for all players!
TGVhZ3VlTWF0Y2hFdmVudC1GYXN0TW92ZQ==.regulation:
Glide through your team's ink faster than ever in swim form. Oh, and try to win the battle while you're at it!

・ Swim-form movement will be greatly increased for all players.
・ Only primary gear abilities will be enabled! Secondary abilities will have no effect.
・ Swim Speed Up gear abilities will have no effect.
